<li><strong>Cru Bourgeois and Petits Châteaux:</strong> 3-8 years</li>
<li><strong>Cru Classé (3rd-5th Growth):</strong> 8-20 years</li>
<li><strong>Super Seconds and First Growths:</strong> 15-40+ years</li>
<li><strong>Exceptional vintages (2005, 2009, 2010):</strong> Add 5-10 years to each category</li>
